#: donation.php:308
msgid "While Stripe doesn't support monthly donations, you can still become a sponsor! Simply make a one-time donation equivalent to 12 months of support, and you'll gain access to the corresponding sponsoring tier. It's an easy and flexible way to contribute."
msgstr "Cé nach dtacaíonn Stripe le síntiúis mhíosúla, is féidir leat a bheith i d’urraitheoir fós! Déan síntiús aonuaire arb ionann é agus 12 mhí de thacaíocht, agus gheobhaidh tú rochtain ar an leibhéal urraíochta comhfhreagrach. Is bealach éasca agus solúbtha é chun ranníocaíocht a dhéanamh."

#: donation.php:311
#, php-format
msgid "Paypal charges up to 35% fee for transactions under $5. For small donations we recommend using other methods."
msgstr "Gearrann Paypal táille suas le 35% ar idirbhearta faoi $5. I gcás síntiúis bheaga molaimid modhanna eile a úsáid."

#: donation.php:316
msgid "If you are not sure or not able to commit to a regular donation, but still want to help the project, you can do a one-time donation, of any amount."
msgstr "Mura bhfuil tú cinnte nó mura bhfuil tú in ann gealltanas a thabhairt síntiús rialta a thabhairt, ach más mian leat cabhrú leis an tionscadal fós, is féidir leat síntiús aonuaire a dhéanamh, d’aon mhéid."

#: donation.php:317
msgid "Choose freely the amount you wish to donate one time only."
msgstr "Roghnaigh go saor an méid is mian leat a bhronnadh uair amháin."

#: donation.php:320
msgid "You can support FreeCAD by sponsoring it as an individual or organization through various platforms. Sponsorship provides a steady income for developers, allowing the FPA to plan ahead and enabling greater investment in FreeCAD. To encourage sponsorship, we offer different tiers, and unless you choose to remain anonymous, your name or company logo will be featured on our website accordingly."
msgstr "Is féidir leat tacú le FreeCAD trína urrú mar dhuine aonair nó mar eagraíocht trí ardáin éagsúla. Soláthraíonn urraíocht ioncam seasta d’fhorbróirí, rud a ligeann don FPA pleanáil roimh ré agus a chuireann ar chumas infheistíocht níos mó i FreeCAD. Chun urraíocht a spreagadh, cuirimid sraitheanna éagsúla ar fáil, agus mura roghnaíonn tú fanacht gan ainm, beidh d’ainm nó lógó do chuideachta le feiceáil ar ár suíomh Gréasáin dá réir."

#: donation.php:324
msgid "Normal sponsor"
msgstr "Urraitheoir gnáth"

#: donation.php:328
msgid "from 1 USD / 1 EUR per month. You will not have your name displayed here, but you will have helped the project a lot anyway. Together, normal sponsors maintain the project on its feet as much as the bigger sponsors."
msgstr "ó 1 USD / 1 EUR in aghaidh na míosa. Ní bheidh d’ainm le feiceáil anseo, ach beidh tú tar éis cabhrú go mór leis an tionscadal ar aon nós. Le chéile, coinníonn urraitheoirí gnáth an tionscadal ar a chosa chomh maith leis na hurraitheoirí níos mó."

#: donation.php:333
msgid "Bronze sponsor"
msgstr "Urraitheoir cré-umha"

#: donation.php:337
msgid "from 25 USD / 25 EUR per month. Your name or company name is displayed on this page."
msgstr "ó 25 USD / 25 EUR in aghaidh na míosa. Taispeántar d’ainm nó ainm do chuideachta ar an leathanach seo."

#: donation.php:342
msgid "Silver sponsor"
msgstr "Urraitheoir airgid"

#: donation.php:346
msgid "from 100 USD / 100 EUR per month. Your name or company name is displayed on this page, with a link to your website, and a one-line description text."
msgstr "ó 100 USD / 100 EUR in aghaidh na míosa. Taispeántar d’ainm nó ainm na cuideachta ar an leathanach seo, mar aon le nasc chuig do shuíomh Gréasáin, agus téacs cur síos aonlíne amháin."

#: donation.php:351
msgid "Gold sponsor"
msgstr "Urraitheoir óir"

#: donation.php:355
msgid "from 200 USD / 200 EUR per month. Your name or company name and logo displayed on this page, with a link to your website and a custom description text. Companies that have helped FreeCAD early on also appear under Gold sponsors."
msgstr "ó 200 USD / 200 EUR in aghaidh na míosa. Taispeántar d'ainm nó ainm agus lógó na cuideachta ar an leathanach seo, mar aon le nasc chuig do shuíomh Gréasáin agus téacs cur síos saincheaptha. Feictear cuideachtaí a chuidigh le FreeCAD go luath faoi urraitheoirí Óir freisin."

#: donation.php:359
msgid "The FPA's <a href=\"https://fpa.freecad.org/handbook/process/accepting-donations.html\">donation rules</a> apply to all donations."
msgstr "Baineann <a href=\"https://fpa.freecad.org/handbook/process/accepting-donations.html\">rialacha síntiús</a> an FPA le gach síntiús."

#: donation.php:360
msgid "Instead of donating each month, you might find it more comfortable to make a one-time donation that, when divided by twelve, would give you right to enter a sponsoring tier. Don't hesitate to do so!"
msgstr "In ionad síntiús a thabhairt gach mí, b’fhéidir go mbeadh sé níos compordaí duit síntiús aonuaire a dhéanamh a thabharfadh, nuair a roinntear é ar a dó dhéag, an ceart duit dul isteach i leibhéal urraíochta. Ná bíodh leisce ort é sin a dhéanamh!"

#: donation.php:361
msgid "Choose freely the amount you wish to donate each month."
msgstr "Roghnaigh go saor an méid is mian leat a bhronnadh gach mí."

#: donation.php:362
msgid "Please inform your forum name or twitter handle as a note in your transfer, or <a href=mailto:fpa@freecad.org>reach to us</a>, so we can give you proper credits!"
msgstr "Cuir d’ainm fóraim nó d’ainm úsáideora Twitter in iúl mar nóta i d’aistriú, nó <a href=mailto:fpa@freecad.org>déan teagmháil linn</a>, ionas gur féidir linn na creidmheasanna cuí a thabhairt duit!"

