#: features.php:66
msgid "Key FreeCAD Features"
msgstr "Príomhghnéithe FreeCAD"

#: features.php:77
msgid "Made to build for the real world"
msgstr "Déanta chun tógáil don saol mór"

#: features.php:79
msgid "FreeCAD is made primarily to design objects for the real world. Everything you do in FreeCAD uses real-world\n"
"              units, be it microns, kilometers, inches or feet, or even any combination of units. FreeCAD offers <a href=https://wiki.freecad.org/Workbenches>tools</a> to produce, export and\n"
"              edit solid, full-precision models, export them for 3D printing or CNC machining, create 2D drawings and views of your models,\n"
"              perform analyses such as Finite Element Analyses, or export model data such as quantities or bills of materials."
msgstr "Tá FreeCAD déanta go príomha chun rudaí a dhearadh don saol réadúil. Úsáideann gach rud a dhéanann tú i FreeCAD aonaid an tsaoil réadúil,\n"
"              bíodh sé ina mhicróin, ina chiliméadair, ina n-orlach nó ina throigh, nó fiú aon teaglaim d'aonaid. Cuireann FreeCAD <a href=https://wiki.freecad.org/Workbenches>uirlisí</a> ar fáil chun samhlacha soladacha, lánchruinneas a tháirgeadh, a onnmhairiú agus a chur in eagar,\n"
"              iad a onnmhairiú le haghaidh priontála 3D nó meaisínithe CNC, líníochtaí 2D agus radhairc de do mhúnlaí a chruthú,\n"
"              anailísí a dhéanamh ar nós Anailísí Eilimintí Críochta, nó sonraí samhail a onnmhairiú ar nós cainníochtaí nó billí ábhar."

#: features.php:97
msgid "A powerful solid-based geometry kernel"
msgstr "Croílár geoiméadrachta cumhachtach atá bunaithe ar sholad"

#: features.php:99
msgid "FreeCAD features an advanced geometry engine based on\n"
"              <a href=https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Open_CASCADE>Open CASCADE Technology</a>. It supports solids,\n"
"              <a href=https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Boundary_representation>Boundary Representation</a> (BRep) objects, and\n"
"              <a href=https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Non-uniform_rational_B-spline>Non-uniform rational basis spline</a> (NURBS)\n"
"              curves and surfaces, and offers a wide range of tools to create and modify these objects, including complex\n"
"              <a href=https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Boolean_operations_on_polygons>Boolean</a> operations,\n"
"              <a href=https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fillet_(mechanics)>fillets</a>, shape cleaning and\n"
"              <a href=https://wiki.freecad.org/OpenCASCADE>much more</a>."
msgstr "Tá inneall geoiméadrachta ardleibhéil ag FreeCAD atá bunaithe ar\n"
"              <a href=https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Open_CASCADE>Teicneolaíocht Oscailte CASCADE</a>. Tacaíonn sé le solaid, réada\n"
"              <a href=https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Boundary_representation>Ionadaíocht Teorann</a> (BRep), agus cuartha agus dromchlaí\n"
"              <a href=https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Non-uniform_rational_B-spline>Splíne bonn réasúnach neamh-aonfhoirmeach</a> (NURBS)\n"
", agus cuireann sé réimse leathan uirlisí ar fáil chun na réada seo a chruthú agus a mhodhnú, lena n-áirítear oibríochtaí casta\n"
"              <a href=https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Boolean_operations_on_polygons>Boolean</a>,\n"
"              <a href=https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fillet_(mechanics)>filléid</a>, glanadh cruthanna agus\n"
"              <a href=https://wiki.freecad.org/OpenCASCADE>i bhfad níos mó</a>."

#: features.php:119
msgid "A wi(l)dly parametric environment"
msgstr "Timpeallacht atá go forleathan paraiméadrach"

#: features.php:121
msgid "All FreeCAD objects are natively parametric, meaning their shape can be based on\n"
"                <a href=\"https://wiki.freecad.org/Property\" title=\"Property\">properties</a> such as numeric values, texts, on/off buttons,\n"
"                or even other objects. All shape changes are recalculated on demand, recorded by an undo/redo stack, and allow to maintain\n"
"                a precise modelling history. Properties of one object can drive the value of properties of other objects, allowing\n"
"                complex, custom parametric chains that could only exist in your wildest dreams. New parametric objects are\n"
"                <a href=https://wiki.freecad.org/Scripted_objects>easy to code</a>."
msgstr "Tá gach réad FreeCAD paraiméadrach dúchasach, rud a chiallaíonn gur féidir a gcruth a bhunú ar\n"
"               <a href=\"https://wiki.freecad.org/Property\" title=\"Property\">airíonna</a> amhail luachanna uimhriúla, téacsanna,\n"
"               cnaipí ar siúl/as,\n"
"               nó fiú réada eile. Déantar gach athrú crutha a athríomh ar éileamh, a thaifeadadh le cruach cealaithe/athdhéanta, agus ligeann siad do stair shamhaltaithe chruinn a choinneáil. Is féidir le hairíonna réada amháin luach airíonna réad eile a thiomáint,\n"
"               rud a ligeann do shlabhraí paraiméadracha casta, saincheaptha a bheith ann nach mbeadh ann ach i do bhrionglóidí is fiáine. Tá réada paraiméadracha nua\n"
"               <a href=https://wiki.freecad.org/Scripted_objects>éasca le códú</a>."

#: features.php:145
msgid "Assembly solutions for every need"
msgstr "Réitigh tionóil do gach riachtanas"

#: features.php:147
msgid "FreeCAD has long offered several great community-made add-on assembly\n"
"                  workbenches that use different solvers and even solver-free workflows to assemble\n"
"                  the parts you create. With FreeCAD 1.0, a new built-in assembly workbench is also\n"
"                  included, based on the\n"
"                  <a href=https://github.com/Ondsel-Development/OndselSolver>Ondsel Solver</a>.\n"
"                  This workbench allows to define 3D constraints between parts, assemble the\n"
"                  different components of a model, and animate everything."
msgstr "Tá roinnt binse oibre tionóil breiseán pobail iontacha á dtairiscint ag FreeCAD le fada an lá a úsáideann\n"
"                   réiteoirí éagsúla agus fiú sreafaí oibre gan réiteoirí chun na codanna a chruthaíonn tú a chur le chéile.\n"
"                   Le FreeCAD 1.0, tá binse oibre tionóil nua ionsuite san áireamh freisin,\n"
"                   bunaithe ar an\n"
"                   <a href=https://github.com/Ondsel-Development/OndselSolver>Ondsel\n"
" Solver</a>.\n"
"                   Ligeann an binse oibre seo srianta 3T a shainiú idir codanna, na\n"
"                   comhpháirteanna éagsúla de shamhaltán a chur le chéile, agus gach rud a bheochan."

#: features.php:170
msgid "Also for architects"
msgstr "Chomh maith le haghaidh ailtirí"

#: features.php:172
msgid "Until version 1.0, FreeCAD had a built-in Arch workbench and\n"
"              an external BIM workbench added on top of that. With version 1.0, both of them have\n"
"              merged and now we have a built-in BIM workbench. Now you can do your building and\n"
"              construction related projects right out of the box."
msgstr "Go dtí leagan 1.0, bhí binse oibre Arch ionsuite i FreeCAD agus\n"
"              binse oibre seachtrach BIM curtha leis. Le leagan 1.0, tá an dá cheann\n"
"              acu cumasctha agus anois tá binse oibre BIM ionsuite againn. Anois is féidir leat do\n"
"              thionscadail tógála agus tógála a dhéanamh díreach as an mbosca."

#: features.php:188
msgid "Python everywhere"
msgstr "Python i ngach áit"

#: features.php:190
msgid "While the FreeCAD core functionality is coded in C++ for robustness and performance,\n"
"                  large parts of the external layers,  workbenches and almost all the communication between\n"
"                  the core and the user interface is coded in <a href=https://python.org>Python</a>,\n"
"                  a flexible, user-friendly, easy to learn programming language. From Python code, you are able to\n"
"                  do just <a href=https://wiki.freecad.org/Power_users_hub>anything in FreeCAD</a>, from simple one-line\n"
"                  commands in the integrated Python console to recording macros, coding your own tools up to\n"
"                  full custom workbenches."
msgstr "Cé go bhfuil feidhmiúlacht lárnach FreeCAD códaithe i C++ ar mhaithe le stóinseacht agus feidhmíocht,\n"
"                  tá codanna móra de na sraitheanna seachtracha, na binse oibre agus beagnach an chumarsáid go léir idir\n"
"                  an croí agus an comhéadan úsáideora códaithe i <a href=https://python.org>Python</a>,\n"
"                  teanga ríomhchlárúcháin sholúbtha, atá furasta a fhoghlaim agus atá furasta a fhoghlaim. Ó chód Python, is féidir leat <a href=https://wiki.freecad.org/Power_users_hub>rud ar bith a dhéanamh\n"
"                  i FreeCAD</a>, ó orduithe simplí aonlíne\n"
"                  sa chonsól Python comhtháite go macraí a thaifeadadh, do chuid uirlisí féin a chódú suas go dtí\n"
"                  binse oibre saincheaptha iomlána."

#: features.php:209
msgid "File formats frenzy"
msgstr "Fuadar formáidí comhaid"

#: features.php:211
msgid "FreeCAD allows you to import and export models and many other kinds of data from your models such as\n"
"              analyses results or quantities data to dozens of different <a href=\"https://wiki.freecad.org/Category:File_Formats\">file formats</a> such as\n"
"              <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISO_10303\">STEP</a>,\n"
"              <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/IGES\">IGES</a>,\n"
"              <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wavefront_.obj_file\">OBJ</a>,\n"
"              <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/STL_%28file_format%29\">STL</a>,\n"
"              <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/.dwg\">DWG</a>,\n"
"              <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dxf\">DXF</a>,\n"
"              <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Svg\">SVG</a>,\n"
"              <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Shapefile\">SHP</a>,\n"
"              <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/COLLADA\">DAE</a>,\n"
"              <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Industry_Foundation_Classes\">IFC</a> or\n"
"              <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/OFF_(file_format)\">OFF</a>,\n"
"              <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/NASTRAN\">NASTRAN</a>,\n"
"              <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/VRML\">VRML</a>,\n"
"              <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/OpenSCAD\">OpenSCAD CSG</a>\n"
"              and many more, in addition to FreeCAD&apos;s native\n"
"              <a href=\"https://wiki.freecad.org/File_Format_FCStd\" title=\"File Format FCStd\">FCStd</a> file format. Add-on workbenches can also add more\n"
"              file formats."
msgstr "Le FreeCAD is féidir leat samhlacha agus go leor cineálacha eile sonraí a allmhairiú agus a onnmhairiú ó do mhúnlaí amhail anailísí,\n"
"              torthaí nó sonraí cainníochtaí chuig mórán formáidí comhaid éagsúla ar nós <a href=\"https://wiki.freecad.org/Category:File_Formats\">STEP</a>,\n"
"              <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISO_10303\">IGES</a>,\n"
"              <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/IGES\">IGES</a>,\n"
"              <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wavefront_.obj_file\">OBJ</a>,\n"
"              <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/STL_%28file_format%29\">STL</a>,\n"
"              <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/.dwg\">DWG</a>,\n"
"              <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dxf\">DXF</a>,\n"
"              <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Svg\">SVG</a>,\n"
"              <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Shapefile\">SHP</a>,\n"
"              <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/COLLADA\">DAE</a>,\n"
"              <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Industry_Foundation_Classes\">IFC</a> nó\n"
"              <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/OFF_(file_format)\">OFF</a>,\n"
"              <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/NASTRAN\">NASTRAN</a>,\n"
"              <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/VRML\">VRML</a>,\n"
"              <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/OpenSCAD\">OpenSCAD CSG</a>\n"
"              agus go leor eile, chomh maith le formáid comhaid dhúchasach FreeCAD\n"
"              <a href=\"https://wiki.freecad.org/File_Format_FCStd\" title=\"File Format FCStd\">FCStd</a>. Is féidir le binse oibre breiseán formáidí comhaid breise\n"
"              a chur leis freisin."

#: features.php:242
msgid "A parametric constraints-based 2D sketcher"
msgstr "Sceitseálaí 2T bunaithe ar shrianta paraiméadracha"

#: features.php:244
msgid "FreeCAD features a state-of-the-art <a href=https://wiki.freecad.org/Sketcher_Workbench>Sketcher</a>\n"
"                  with integrated constraint-solver, allowing you to sketch geometry-constrained 2D shapes. Sketches are the main\n"
"                  building block of FreeCAD, and the constrained 2D shapes built with it may then be used as a base to build other\n"
"                  objects throughout FreeCAD, be it either with the\n"
"                  dedicated <a href=https://wiki.freecad.org/PartDesign_Workbench>Part Design workbench</a> or any other workbench."
msgstr "Tá <a href=https://wiki.freecad.org/Sketcher_Workbench>Sketcher</a>\n"
"                  den scoth i FreeCAD le réiteoir srianta comhtháite, rud a ligeann duit cruthanna 2T atá srianta ag geoiméadracht a sceitseáil. Is iad sceitsí\n"
"                  príomhbhloc\n"
"                  tógála FreeCAD, agus is féidir na cruthanna 2T srianta a thógtar leis a úsáid mar bhonn chun \n"
"                  rudaí eile a thógáil ar fud FreeCAD, bíodh sé leis an <a href=https://wiki.freecad.org/PartDesign_Workbench>binse oibre Dearaidh Páirteanna</a> tiomnaithe nó le haon bhinse oibre eile."

#: features.php:262
msgid "A large (and growing) multi-specialty ecosystem"
msgstr "Éiceachóras il-speisialtachta mór (agus atá ag fás)"

#: features.php:264
msgid "FreeCAD offers dedicated <a href=\"https://wiki.freecad.org/Workbenches\">workbenches</a> for a variety of purposes\n"
"              such as\n"
"              <a href=\"https://wiki.freecad.org/Part_Workbench\">CSG modeling</a>,\n"
"              simple <a href=\"https://wiki.freecad.org/Draft_Workbench\">2D CAD drafting</a>,\n"
"              <a href=\"https://wiki.freecad.org/Surface_Module\">NURBS surfaces</a>,\n"
"              <a href=\"https://wiki.freecad.org/Arch_Module\">architectural or BIM modeling</a>,\n"
"              <a href=\"https://wiki.freecad.org/Path_Workbench\">3D printing, CAM and CNC</a>,\n"
"              <a href=\"https://wiki.freecad.org/Points_Module\">point clouds</a>,\n"
"              working with <a href=\"https://wiki.freecad.org/OpenSCAD_Module\">OpenSCAD files</a>,\n"
"              designing <a href=\"https://wiki.freecad.org/Robot_Workbench\">industrial robot trajectories</a>,\n"
"              doing <a href=\"https://wiki.freecad.org/FEM_Module\">Finite Element Analyses</a>,\n"
"              and much more. FreeCAD also provides easy tools to install and manage\n"
"              <a href=\"https://wiki.freecad.org/External_workbenches\">add-on workbenches</a> and\n"
"              <a href=\"https://wiki.freecad.org/Macros_recipes\">macros</a> developed by the users\n"
"              community."
msgstr "Cuireann FreeCAD <a href=\"https://wiki.freecad.org/Workbenches\">binse oibre</a> tiomnaithe ar fáil le haghaidh réimse críocha\n"
"                   amhail\n"
"                   <a href=\"https://wiki.freecad.org/Part_Workbench\">samhalta CSG</a>,\n"
"                   <a href=\"https://wiki.freecad.org/Draft_Workbench\">dréachtú CAD 2T simplí</a>,\n"
"                   <a href=\"https://wiki.freecad.org/Surface_Module\">dromchlaí NURBS</a>,\n"
"                   <a href=\"https://wiki.freecad.org/Arch_Module\">samhalta ailtireachta nó BIM</a>,\n"
"                   <a href=\"https://wiki.freecad.org/Path_Workbench\">priontáil 3T, CAM agus CNC</a>,\n"
"                   <a href=\"https://wiki.freecad.org/Points_Module\">scamall pointe</a>,\n"
"                   oibriú le <a href=\"https://wiki.freecad.org/OpenSCAD_Module\">OpenSCAD comhaid</a>,\n"
"                   dearadh <a href=\"https://wiki.freecad.org/Robot_Workbench\">conairí róbat tionsclaíocha</a>,\n"
"                   déanamh <a href=\"https://wiki.freecad.org/FEM_Module\">Anailísí ar Eilimintí Críochta</a>,\n"
"                   agus i bhfad níos mó. Soláthraíonn FreeCAD uirlisí éasca freisin chun\n"
"                  <a href=\"https://wiki.freecad.org/External_workbenches\">binse oibre breise</a> agus\n"
"                   <a href=\"https://wiki.freecad.org/Macros_recipes\">macra</a> arna bhforbairt ag\n"
"                  pobal na n-úsáideoirí a shuiteáil agus a bhainistiú."

#: features.php:280
msgid "https://wiki.freecad.org/Feature_list"
msgstr "https://wiki.freecad.org/Feature_list"

#: features.php:294
msgid "Developed by a community"
msgstr "Forbartha ag pobal"

#: features.php:296
msgid "FreeCAD is made for everybody, by everybody. It is developed and maintained\n"
"              by a community of developers, users, moderators, translators, all united by their wish make\n"
"              FreeCAD a free and powerful tool. There is no commercial aim behind decisions being taken, no\n"
"              urge to make you upgrade your version of FreeCAD or to corner you into a specific workflow or\n"
"              ecosystem. FreeCAD and the files and data you produce with FreeCAD are truly yours, forever."
msgstr "Tá FreeCAD déanta do chách, ag cách. Forbraítear agus cothabháiltear é ag pobal forbróirí,\n"
"                  úsáideoirí, modhnóirí, aistritheoirí, agus iad uile aontaithe ag a mianta, rud a fhágann gur uirlis shaor agus chumhachtach é \n"
"                  FreeCAD. Níl aon aidhm tráchtála taobh thiar de chinntí atá á ndéanamh, níl aon á\n"
"                  teamh ann go n-uasghrádófá do leagan de FreeCAD nó go gcuirfí i bhfeidhm sreabha oibre nó\n"
"                  éiceachóras ar leith thú. Is leatsa FreeCAD agus na comhaid agus na sonraí a tháirgeann tú le FreeCAD go deo."

