#: index.php:114
msgid "Create 3D from 2D & back"
msgstr "Cruthaigh 3T ó 2T & ar ais"

#: index.php:116
msgid "FreeCAD allows you to sketch geometry constrained 2D shapes and use\n"
"          them as a base to build other objects. It contains many components\n"
"          to adjust dimensions or extract design details from 3D models to\n"
"          create high quality production ready drawings."
msgstr "Le FreeCAD is féidir leat cruthanna 2T srianta geoiméadracha a sceitseáil agus iad a úsáid\n"
"                  mar bhonn chun rudaí eile a thógáil. Tá go leor comhpháirteanna\n"
"                  ann chun toisí a choigeartú nó sonraí dearaidh a bhaint as \n"
"                  samhlacha 3T chun líníochtaí ardchaighdeáin réidh le haghaidh táirgeachta a chruthú."

#: index.php:135
msgid "For professional design needs..."
msgstr "Le haghaidh riachtanais dearaidh ghairmiúla..."

#: index.php:137
msgid "FreeCAD is a powerful and evolving open-source parametric 3D modeler, well-suited for many professional and technical tasks. With the release of version 1.0, it marks a new milestone in stability and usability. FreeCAD puts you in control - no licensing fees, no vendor lock-in. It's not just cost-effective - it’s yours to adapt and build upon."
msgstr "Is samhaltóir paraiméadrach 3T foinse oscailte cumhachtach agus atá ag teacht chun cinn é FreeCAD, atá oiriúnach do go leor tascanna gairmiúla agus teicniúla. Le heisiúint leagan 1.0, marcálann sé cloch mhíle nua i gcobhsaíocht agus inúsáidteacht. Tugann FreeCAD smacht duit - gan aon táillí ceadúnaithe, gan aon ghlasáil díoltóra. Ní hamháin go bhfuil sé cost-éifeachtach - is leatsa é a oiriúnú agus tógáil air."

#: index.php:144
msgid "Baked by Kris Wilk"
msgstr "Bácáilte ag Kris Wilk"

#: index.php:155
msgid "...And for everything else"
msgstr "...Agus i gcás gach rud eile"

#: index.php:157
msgid "Whether you're prototyping, 3D printing, designing furniture, or learning CAD, FreeCAD offers the tools to support your creativity. With a strong community, extensive documentation, and a growing ecosystem of add-ons, it’s a great place to start - and to grow. No sign-up, no paywall, no restrictions. Just open-source freedom at your fingertips."
msgstr "Cibé acu atá tú ag déanamh fréamhshamhlacha, ag priontáil 3T, ag dearadh troscáin, nó ag foghlaim CAD, cuireann FreeCAD na huirlisí ar fáil chun tacú le do chruthaitheacht. Le pobal láidir, doiciméadacht fhairsing, agus éiceachóras breiseán atá ag fás, is áit iontach é le tosú - agus le fás. Gan chlárú, gan bhalla pá, gan srianta. Saoirse foinse oscailte ar fáil go héasca."

#: index.php:163
msgid "Modelled by epileftric"
msgstr "Samhlaithe ag epileftric"

#: index.php:168
msgid "Accessible, flexible & integrated"
msgstr "Inrochtana, solúbtha & comhtháite"

#: index.php:170
msgid "FreeCAD is a multiplatform (Windows, Mac and Linux), highly\n"
"          customizable and extensible software. It reads and writes to many\n"
"          open file formats such as STEP, IGES, STL, SVG, DXF, OBJ, IFC, DAE\n"
"          and many others, making it possible to seamlessly integrate it into\n"
"          your workflow."
msgstr "Is bogearraí il-ardáin (Windows, Mac agus Linux) é FreeCAD atá an-shaincheaptha\n"
"                  agus inleathnaithe. Léann agus scríobhann sé chuig go leor formáidí comhaid\n"
"                  oscailte ar nós STEP, IGES, STL, SVG, DXF, OBJ, IFC, DAE\n"
"                  agus go leor eile, rud a fhágann gur féidir é a chomhtháthú go gan uaim i do shr\n"
"                  abhadh oibre."

#: index.php:180
msgid "Modelled by regis"
msgstr "Samhlaithe ag regis"

#: index.php:185
msgid "Designed for your needs"
msgstr "Deartha do do riachtanais"

#: index.php:187
msgid "FreeCAD is designed to fit a wide range of uses including product\n"
"          design, mechanical engineering and architecture. Whether you are a\n"
"          hobbyist, a programmer, an experienced CAD user, a student or a\n"
"          teacher, you will feel right at home with FreeCAD."
msgstr "Tá FreeCAD deartha chun freastal ar raon leathan úsáidí lena n-áirítear dearadh\n"
"                  táirgí, innealtóireacht mheicniúil agus ailtireacht. Cibé acu caitheamh aimsire thú,\n"
"                  ríomhchláraitheoir, úsáideoir CAD a bhfuil taithí aige, mac léinn nó\n"
"                  múinteoir, beidh tú ar do shuaimhneas le FreeCAD."

#: index.php:196
msgid "Modelled by rider_mortagnais"
msgstr "Samhlaithe ag rider_mortagnais"

#: index.php:201
msgid "And many more great features"
msgstr "Agus go leor gnéithe iontacha eile"

#: index.php:203
msgid "FreeCAD equips you with all the right tools for your needs. You get\n"
"          modern Finite Element Analysis (FEA) tools, experimental CFD, dedicated BIM,\n"
"          Geodata or CAM/CNC workbenches, a robot simulation module that\n"
"          allows you to study robot movements and many more features. FreeCAD\n"
"          really is a Swiss Army knife of general-purpose engineering\n"
"          toolkits."
msgstr "Cuireann FreeCAD na huirlisí cearta ar fáil duit do do chuid riachtanas. Gheobhaidh tú uirlisí\n"
"                  nua-aimseartha um Anailís Eilimintí Críochta (FEA),\n"
"                  CFD turgnamhach, BIM tiomnaithe, binse oibre Geodata nó CAM/CNC,\n"
"                  modúl insamhalta róbat a ligeann duit gluaiseachtaí róbat a scrúdú agus go leor gnéithe eile.\n"
"                  Is scian Arm na hEilvéise de threalamh innealtóireachta ilchuspóireacha é\n"
"                  FreeCAD i ndáiríre."

#: index.php:217
msgid "Modelled by bejant"
msgstr "Samhlaithe ag bejant"

#: index.php:222
msgid "Want to contribute to FreeCAD?"
msgstr "Ar mhaith leat cur le FreeCAD?"

#: index.php:224
msgid "FreeCAD is a truly open source project and if you would like to help\n"
"          fix bugs, implement new cool features or work on the documentation,\n"
"          we invite you to join us and create a software that benefits the\n"
"          whole community."
msgstr "Is tionscadal foinse oscailte i ndáiríre é FreeCAD agus más mian leat cabhrú\n"
"                  le fabhtanna a shocrú, gnéithe nua fionnuara a chur i bhfeidhm nó oibriú ar an doiciméadú,\n"
"                  tugaimid cuireadh duit páirt a ghlacadh linn \n"
"                  agus bogearraí a chruthú a rachaidh chun tairbhe an phobail ar fad."

#: index.php:230
msgid "Get involved"
msgstr "Bí páirteach"

#: professional-network.php:14
msgid "Join the community shaping the future of FreeCAD."
msgstr "Bí páirteach sa phobal atá ag múnlú todhchaí FreeCAD."

#: professional-network.php:23
msgid "The FreeCAD Professional Network (FPN) is a voluntary association of professionals committed to strengthening the FreeCAD ecosystem for long-term growth and success."
msgstr "Is cumann deonach gairmithe é Líonra Gairmiúil FreeCAD (FPN) atá tiomanta d'éiceachóras FreeCAD a neartú le haghaidh fáis agus rath fadtéarmach."

#: professional-network.php:26
msgid "If FreeCAD is part of your livelihood—whether you design, teach, manufacture, research, or create content—the FPN is your place to connect, collaborate, and make an impact."
msgstr "Más cuid de do shlí bheatha é FreeCAD—cibé acu atá tú ag dearadh, ag múineadh, ag monarú, ag taighde, nó ag cruthú ábhair—is é an FPN an áit duit chun ceangal, comhoibriú agus tionchar a imirt."

