#: professional-network.php:52
msgid "The FPN brings professionals together to:"
msgstr "Tugann an FPN gairmithe le chéile chun:"

#: professional-network.php:54
msgid "Advocate for features and improvements that matter most"
msgstr "Abhcóideacht ar son na ngnéithe agus na bhfeabhsuithe is tábhachtaí"

#: professional-network.php:55
msgid "Help set priorities for FreeCAD development"
msgstr "Cabhraigh le tosaíochtaí a shocrú le haghaidh forbairt FreeCAD"

#: professional-network.php:56
msgid "Provide domain expertise directly to maintainers and contributors"
msgstr "Saineolas fearainn a sholáthar go díreach do chothaitheoirí agus do rannpháirtithe"

#: professional-network.php:57
msgid "Organize real-world meetups and events"
msgstr "Eagraigh cruinnithe agus imeachtaí sa saol fíor"

#: professional-network.php:58
msgid "Share knowledge, best practices, and support"
msgstr "Eolas, dea-chleachtais agus tacaíocht a roinnt"

#: professional-network.php:59
msgid "Co-develop tools and solutions for the community"
msgstr "Comhfhorbairt uirlisí agus réitigh don phobal"

#: professional-network.php:62
msgid "This is where professionals make their voice heard and pool their strengths to move FreeCAD forward."
msgstr "Seo an áit a gcuireann gairmithe a nglór in iúl agus a dtagann siad le chéile chun FreeCAD a bhogadh ar aghaidh."

