#: professional-network.php:112
msgid "Membership isn't just a fee—it's an investment in FreeCAD's future and in your own professional ecosystem."
msgstr "Ní táille amháin atá i mballraíocht—is infheistíocht í i dtodhchaí FreeCAD agus i d’éiceachóras gairmiúil féin."

#: professional-network.php:120
msgid "Why Join?"
msgstr "Cén fáth a mbeadh tú páirteach?"

#: professional-network.php:121
msgid "Because FreeCAD is already part of your professional life. Together, we can:"
msgstr "Ós rud é gur cuid de do shaol gairmiúil é FreeCAD cheana féin. Le chéile, is féidir linn:"

#: professional-network.php:123
msgid "Influence its direction"
msgstr "Tionchar a imirt ar a threo"

#: professional-network.php:124
msgid "Create an ecosystem that is friendly to commercial interest"
msgstr "Éiceachóras a chruthú atá cairdiúil do leas tráchtála"

#: professional-network.php:125
msgid "Build stronger connections across industries"
msgstr "Naisc níos láidre a thógáil idir tionscail"

#: professional-network.php:126
msgid "Ensure FreeCAD continues to thrive as a tool you can rely on"
msgstr "Cinntigh go leanann FreeCAD ag rathú mar uirlis ar féidir leat brath uirthi"

#: sponsor.php:57
msgid "Donating and sponsoring"
msgstr "Deonú agus urraíocht"

#: sponsor.php:64
msgid "Donating to FreeCAD"
msgstr "Ag tabhairt síntiús do FreeCAD"

#: sponsor.php:69
msgid "Thanks for your interest in helping the FreeCAD\n"
"              project with donations."
msgstr "Go raibh maith agat as do spéis i gcabhrú le tionscadal FreeCAD\n"
"              le síntiúis."

#: sponsor.php:73
msgid "FreeCAD is a fast-growing project, developed by a\n"
"              community of developers and users working mostly on a voluntary\n"
"              basis, motivated mainly by their will to build a great, free 3D\n"
"              parametric modeller. The development of FreeCAD happens mostly\n"
"              because of the energy of all these people, without the need for\n"
"              money."
msgstr "Is tionscadal atá ag fás go mear é FreeCAD, arna fhorbairt\n"
"                  ag pobal forbróirí agus úsáideoirí atá ag obair den chuid is mó ar\n"
"                  bhonn deonach, spreagtha den chuid is mó ag a dtoil samhaltóir paraiméadrach 3D\n"
"                  iontach, saor in aisce a thógáil. Tarlaíonn forbairt FreeCAD den chuid is mó mar g\n"
"                  eall ar fhuinneamh na ndaoine seo go léir, gan aon ghá\n"
"                  le hairgead."

#: sponsor.php:81
msgid "However, money can help the project to achieve many\n"
"              other goals. It can help some of its developers to work more\n"
"              frequently or more regularly on the project, by paying for their\n"
"              time so they can dedicate more of it to FreeCAD, or it can help\n"
"              the community to send people to CAD-related events, so we can\n"
"              showcase FreeCAD and interest professional users. It can also help\n"
"              to organize events ourselves so community members can meet, pay for\n"
"              server space and web services, and many other things."
msgstr "Mar sin féin, is féidir le hairgead cabhrú leis an tionscadal go leor\n"
"                  spriocanna eile a bhaint amach. Is féidir leis cabhrú le cuid dá fhorbróirí oibriú\n"
"                  níos minice nó níos rialta ar an tionscadal, trí íoc as a gcuid ama ionas gur féidir leo níos mó de a thiomnú do FreeCAD, nó is féidir leis cabhrú leis an\n"
"                  bpobal daoine a sheoladh chuig imeachtaí a\n"
"                  bhaineann le CAD, ionas gur féidir linn FreeCAD\n"
"                  a chur i láthair agus spéis a mhúscailt in úsáideoirí gairmiúla. Is féidir leis cabhrú\n"
"                  freisin imeachtaí a eagrú muid féin ionas gur féidir le baill an phobail bualadh le chéile, íoc as spás\n"
"                  freastalaí agus seirbhísí gréasáin, agus go leor rudaí eile."

#: sponsor.php:91
msgid "There are several ways you can donate money and help\n"
"              the FreeCAD project, being an individual, a company or an\n"
"              institution, depending on your preferences. The money you donate\n"
"              to the FreeCAD project will be received and handled by the\n"
"              <a href=https://fpa.freecad.org>FreeCAD Project Association</a>\n"
"              (FPA), a non-profit association created by FreeCAD administrators\n"
"              and core developers. The FPA will redistribute the money it gathers\n"
"              to FreeCAD developers and sponsor itself several projects, efforts\n"
"              and ideas to fuel the development of FreeCAD."
msgstr "Tá roinnt bealaí ann ar féidir leat airgead a bhronnadh agus cabhrú\n"
"                  leis an tionscadal FreeCAD, mar dhuine aonair, mar chuideachta nó mar\n"
"                  institiúid, ag brath ar do chuid sainroghanna.\n"
"                  Glacfaidh agus láimhseálfaidh an\n"
"                  <a href=https://fpa.freecad.org>FreeCAD Project Association</a> (FPA),\n"
"                  cumann neamhbhrabúis a chruthaigh riarthóirí FreeCAD agus\n"
"                  forbróirí lárnacha, an t-airgead a bhronnann tú ar an tionscadal FreeCAD.\n"
"                  Déanfaidh an FPA an t-airgead a bhailíonn sé a athdháileadh ar fhorbróirí FreeCAD agus déanfaidh sé urraíocht ar roinnt tionscadal,\n"
"                  iarrachtaí agus smaointe chun forbairt FreeCAD a chothú."

#: sponsor.php:102
msgid "Remember, however: FreeCAD is free, and will always\n"
"              be free. You are not required, and never will be, to donate anything\n"
"              in order to use FreeCAD, neither to modify or distribute it. Your\n"
"              donation will be welcome, and can help a lot, but you will never\n"
"              be required to pay anything to access any of the FreeCAD features."
msgstr "Cuimhnigh, áfach: tá FreeCAD saor in aisce,\n"
"              agus beidh sé saor in aisce i gcónaí. Ní gá duit, agus ní bheidh ort choíche, aon rud\n"
"              a bhronnadh chun FreeCAD a úsáid, ná é a mhodhnú ná a dháileadh. Cuirfear fáilte roimh do bhronntanas,\n"
"              agus is féidir leis cabhrú go mór, ach ní gá duit aon rud a íoc\n"
"              chun rochtain a fháil ar aon cheann de ghnéithe FreeCAD."

